b_tor_vacuum_aos3.b0.documentation: Vacuum toroidal field at b0. Positive sign means anti-clockwise when viewed from above. The product r0*b0 must be consistent with the b_tor_vacuum_r field of the tf IDS.

b_tor_vacuum_aos3.r0_error_index.documentation: Index in the error_description list for "r0"

b_tor_vacuum_aos3.r0.documentation: Reference major radius where the vacuum toroidal magnetic field is given (usually a fixed position such as the middle of the vessel at the equatorial midplane)

b_tor_vacuum_aos3.documentation: Characteristics of the vacuum toroidal field, dynamic within a type 3 AoS

b_tor_vacuum_aos3.b0_error_index.documentation: Index in the error_description list for "b0"
